1. Copy an array of numbers from the internet and code that e.g. prints out the numbers. 

2. Edit the code of #1, e.g. edit the number range, print every other element, print every third element, 
print numbers from largest to smallest and from smallest to largest 

3. Do some of the tasks of #1 and #2 using both for and while loops, also try do-while.

4. Ask the user for the number range, there must be x-number of numbers in between (come up with x yourself or ask the user). 
Check if the numbers entered by the user fall within the number range, calculate the sum and average of the numbers 
entered by the user.